transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Tom Viagra speaking, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Hi, good afternoon, this is Tom Savarese.

Speaker 1: I've been getting this order deliveries of Viagra,

Speaker 2: They're sending me like,

Speaker 2: yeah, you can get this when you need it,

Speaker 2: I'll put it down so I can help you out, one moment.

Speaker 1: Okay. Is your name Tom?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: One second, sir.

Speaker 2: All right, yeah, Tom, I mean, either we can set up

Speaker 2: that's totally up to you.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I do as needed,

Speaker 1: because I have like five bottles right now.

Speaker 2: Okay, so basically how that works,

Speaker 2: And you'll have to call us for your next order there.

Speaker 1: Right.

Speaker 2: Okay, yeah, we'll do that for now.

Speaker 1: If you'd like, I can even give you my extension.

Speaker 2: I can place those orders for you,

Speaker 1: and make sure that your account, you know,

Speaker 2: stays the way you want it, if you'd like.

Speaker 1: Okay, that'd be great.

Speaker 2: All right, so the name is Quinn, Q-U-I-N-N.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: And my extension is 0035.

Speaker 1: 0035, okay, great.

Speaker 2: All right, well, you are all set other than that, sir.

Speaker 1: Did you get my name and stuff, or?

Speaker 1: Oh, phone number, okay, great.

Speaker 2: All right, have a, have a receipt, yeah.

Speaker 1: Have a receipt, okay.

Speaker 2: Yes, you are all set, sir.
